      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30660620&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=679&rangeEnd=886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5c32bd071d3d80ce5c7d1e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=679&rangeEnd=886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30660620_6_437-792",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "437-792",
      "markText": "青青河畔草，郁郁园中柳。 盈盈楼上女，皎皎当窗牖。 娥娥红粉妆，纤纤出素手。 昔为倡家女，今为荡子妇。 荡子行不归，空床难独守。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30660620&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=437&rangeEnd=792",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5c32bd071d3d80ce5c7d1e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=437&rangeEnd=792"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30660620_5_4204-4250",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4204-4250",
      "markText": "这种回环复沓，是歌谣的生命；许多歌谣没有韵，专靠这种组织来建筑它们的体格，表现那强度的情感。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30660620&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4204&rangeEnd=4250",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5c32bd071d3d80ce5c7d1e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4204&rangeEnd=4250"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30660620_23_439-794",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "439-794",
      "markText": "明月何皎皎，照我罗床帏。 忧愁不能寐，揽衣起徘徊。 客行虽云乐，不如早旋归。 出户独彷徨，愁思当告谁。 引领还入房，泪下沾裳衣。",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30660620&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=439&rangeEnd=794",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5c32bd071d3d80ce5c7d1e?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=439&rangeEnd=794"
    },
